title: 공역 0 위에서 실험하기 | Experimenting on Codomain Zero
description: This project explores how quantum circuits may develop structure from codomain-zero — a state of unassigned potential. Based on feedback-guided experiments discussed in the 2025-05-10 session, this documentation outlines structural behavior when circuits resist or fail to organize, offering a new definition of 'zero' in quantum frameworks.
